high_descs: go to the diningtable.
pick up the knife from top of the table.
walk to the hallway and find the potato that is on the floor.
Cut the potato in the box and then close the box.
walk to the hallway and go in the bed.
Put the knife on the bed.
turn around and go into the hallway to where the potato is.
pick up the potato from the box and close the box.
walk through the hall to get to the microwave.
Walk around the kitchen and look for a spot to put the potato on the counter.
take the potato to the diningtable.
Put the potato down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take the potato from the box and find a place to put it on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn around to the diningtable.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Go to the potato and turn right, then turn left at the dresser, go to the cardboard box on the floor.
Slice the potato in the cardboard box.
Go toward the dresser turn left, go across the room to the bed.
Place the knife on the bed.
Head back to the cardboard box.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Go toward the dresser, turn right, go to the end of the hall and turn left, go across to the microwave.
Place the potato slice in the microwave, heat the potato, and pick the potato back up.
Turn around to the diningtable.
Place the potato on the diningtable behind the glass bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of Potato on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the opposite side of the diningtable in front.
Pick up the knife from the round table.
Move to the left side of the potato, head to a corridor that is in front, take a first exit on the right, then first available turn to the left, and stop before a box on the floor.
Cut the potato with the knife in the box and close it.
Turn around, walk straight to the wall, turn left and go to the bed across the room.
Place the knife on the bed.
Go back to the potato on the floor.
Take a potato slice out of the box and close the box.
Go back to the starting room and move all the way to the other end with the microwave.
Put the potato slice in the microwave, heat the potato up for a bit, then take it out.
Turn around and go to the diningtable.
Place the potato slice on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated-up potato on the diningtable
